ned within the bottom geometry\n    for x, y in sorted_vertices[:2]:\n        offset_y = y - tol\n        if not bottom_geom.contains_point(x, offset_y):\n            return False\n    return True\n```\n\n**Key Physics:**\n- Tolerance of 0.025 units allows for small penetration/floating\n- Only checks bottom 2 vertices (handles rectangles correctly)\n- Checks containment after offsetting down by tolerance (ensures stability)\n\n---\n\n### Key Constants Summary\n\n| Parameter | Value | Notes |\n|-----------|-------|-------|\n| **World** | | |\n| world_max_x | 1.618 | Golden ratio |\n| world_max_y | 1.0 | |\n| **Robot** | | |\n| base_radius | 0.1 | Circle base |\n| arm_length | 0.2 | 2 × base_radius |\n| gripper_height | 0.07 | Vacuum end-effector |\n| gripper_width | 0.01 | |\n| **Vacuum** | | |\n| vacuum_threshold | 0.5 | Values ≥0.5 activate suction |\n| **Target Block** | | |\n| width_range | [0.05, 0.2] | Randomized |\n| height_range | [0.05, 0.2] | Randomized |\n| **Obstructions (o4)** | | |\n| count | 4 | Per Obstruction2D-o4-v0 |\n| init_on_target_prob | 0.9 | 90% placed on surface |\n| **Termination** | | |\n| is_on tolerance | 0.025 | Vertical offset check |"}],"totalDurationMs":30844,"totalTokens":26885,"totalToolUseCount":6,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":17523,"cache_read_input_tokens":7105,"output_tokens":2251,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":17523},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
